        <div class="container px-3">

            <div class="row gx-4 justify-content-center">
            
                <div class = 'container_modale_recommandations'>

                    <div id="presentation_text" class="col-lg-12">

                        <h2>Steam 2024 Promotion Campaign</h2>

                        <p class="lead">As part of a final-year university project in the BUT Data Science program, we were asked to develop a complete web application. After several searches for relevant and valuable datasets, we decided to exploit a set of information linked to the Steam platform. Steam is an online content distribution platform, offering a wide range of video games. Passionate about this universe, we sought to approach this content in a professional manner.</p>

                        <a type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="button_start_now" href ="#problematic">Start Now</a>

                    </div>

                    <div>

                        <img src="{{asset("icons/Home_Jeux.PNG")}}"></img>

                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </section>

